## How to apply this license to your repo

1. Create a file named `LICENSE` (no extension) at the repository root and paste the text above. Replace the `[Your Name]`, `[Your Jurisdiction]`, and contact email.
2. Commit & push:

```bash
git add LICENSE
git commit -m "Add Hedge Engine Personal Use License (HE-PUL) v1.0"
git push
```

3. In your README add a short note:
   `License: Hedge Engine Personal Use License (HE-PUL) v1.0 — see LICENSE for full terms.`

